stateDiagram-v2
    [*] --> stable

    stable --> stressed: anomaly_density > threshold_1\nOR pruning_rate_7d > threshold_2

    stressed --> critical: anomaly_density > threshold_3\nOR cascade_events > threshold_4\nOR consensus_rate < threshold_5

    critical --> recovery: anomaly_density < threshold_1\nAND consensus_rate > threshold_5\n(sustained 24h)

    recovery --> stable: pruning_rate < threshold_2\nAND entropy in healthy range\n(sustained 72h)

    note right of critical: All channels tighten\nto max restriction
